name: Whimsical Statement Necklaces

Each necklace is packaged on a tag card with a quote that enhances the necklace.

Globe - “Be the change you wish to see in the world.” – Mahatma Gandhi
Heart – “The best and most wonderful things in the world cannot be seen or even touched – they must be felt with the heart.” – Helen Keller
Hot Air Balloon – “The biggest adventure you can take is to live the life of your dreams.” – Oprah Winfrey

Heart – 27” brass colored chain, 1.5”x1.75” heart pendant
Hot Air Balloon – 28” rose gold tone chain, 3”x1.25” balloon pendant
Globe - 32” brass colored chain, 1.75”x1.25” globe pendant, .75”x.75” binocular charm
